<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/170246-why-do-the-sisters-like-eachother-so-much">why do the sisters like EACHOTHER SO MUCH?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_170246'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F11208.How_the_Garc_a_Girls_Lost_Their_Accents">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/170246-why-do-the-sisters-like-eachother-so-much">6 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/170246-why-do-the-sisters-like-eachother-so-much">Add your answer</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/95863343-genevieve"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1612391696i/95863343._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/95863343-genevieve">Genevieve</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I&apos;m not sure they do. They seem to be bound by being sisters as opposed to any friendly feelings towards one another as adults, and as kids, it seems <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I'm not sure they do. They seem to be bound by being sisters as opposed to any friendly feelings towards one another as adults, and as kids, it seems more that they band together in the way many siblings do, out of necessity or proximity.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerFooter'>

